         <div xml:id="alalal-h85023"><!-- l4d21a3 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-h85023-Hd1e99">Articulus 3</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-h85023-Hd1e101" type="question-title">An lignum, fenum, stipula, edificentur
super fundamentum ?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h85023-d1e104">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="50"/>ARTICULUS III.
<lb ed="#Be" n="51"/>An lignum, fenum, stipula, edificentur
<lb ed="#Be" n="52"/>super fundamentum ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h85023-d1e113">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="53"/>Deinde queritur de hoc quod dicit,
<lb ed="#Be" n="54"/>ibi, A, post medium: <quote xml:id="alalal-h85023-Qd1e119"> Qui 
xdificave<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="55"/>runt lignum, fenum, stipulam, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h85023-d1e125">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="56"/>Videtur enim, quod super 
fundamen<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="57"/>tum talia non edificentur : quia fides
<lb ed="#Be" n="58"/>non habet ordinem nisi ad bona opera :
<lb ed="#Be" n="59"/>sed venialia non sunt opera bona : ergo
<lb ed="#Be" n="60"/>videtur, quod non edificentur super
<lb ed="#Be" n="61"/>fidem.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h85023-d1e142">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="62"/>Ad hoc dicendum, quod spiritualis
<lb ed="#Be" n="63"/>edificii fundamentum in imo est fides,
<lb ed="#Be" n="64"/>que facit in nobis subsistere res 
speran<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="65"/>das, eo quod ipsa est prima accedentibus
<lb ed="#Be" n="66"/>ad Deum : sed.in summo concludens est
<lb ed="#Be" n="67"/>charitas, quae est vinculum perfectionis :
<lb ed="#Be" n="68"/>et paries erigens, est spes se ad aeterna
<lb ed="#Be" n="69"/>protendens. Cardinales autem sunt 
mate<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="70"/>ria, quae dant substantiam edificio : et
<lb ed="#Be" n="71"/>materia super fundamentum esse dicitur
<lb ed="#Be" n="72"/>tantum tripliciter, scilicet directo situ,
<lb ed="#Be" n="73"/>et sic nihil edificatur nisi bona opera.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h85023-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="74"/>Dicitur etiam super, id est, juxta,
<lb ed="#Be" n="75"/>sicut ibi, Super flumina Babylonis,
<lb ed="#Be" n="76"/>etc. : et sic venialia superedificantur.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h85023-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="77"/>Tertio dicitur super, id est, post, 
sic<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="78"/>ut, Ezechiel. xuviu, 3: <quote xml:id="alalal-h85023-Qd1e186">Super terminum |
<lb ed="#Be" n="79"/>Aser</quote>, etc. Dicit Glossa, id est, post 
ter<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="80"/>minum Aser.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h85023-d1e194">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="81"/>Et sic mortalia superedificantur, 
se<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="82"/>cundum expositionem Hieronymi supra
<lb ed="#Be" n="83"/>inductam,
</p>
         </div>
